[
  {
    "id": "p-cf3e32",
    "offset": 0,
    "text": "**Vishnu Smriti 85**"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-a49b09",
    "offset": 22,
    "text": "Now, a *śrāddha* (श्राद्ध) performed at Puṣkara is imperishable. // Vi_85.1 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-58b9d5",
    "offset": 102,
    "text": "And so are muttered prayers, oblations, and austerities. // Vi_85.2 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-4d0647",
    "offset": 174,
    "text": "By merely bathing at Puṣkara, one is purified from all sins. // Vi_85.3 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-3e875d",
    "offset": 250,
    "text": "Likewise at Gayāśīrṣa. // Vi_85.4 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-4d57f6",
    "offset": 288,
    "text": "At the Vaṭa (banyan tree). // Vi_85.5 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-7a4cd4",
    "offset": 330,
    "text": "On the Amarakaṇṭaka mountain. // Vi_85.6 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-b74e09",
    "offset": 375,
    "text": "On the Varāha mountain. // Vi_85.7 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-f954ce",
    "offset": 414,
    "text": "Anywhere on the bank of the Narmadā. // Vi_85.8 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-7c8df8",
    "offset": 466,
    "text": "On the bank of the Yamunā. // Vi_85.9 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-56eece",
    "offset": 508,
    "text": "And especially on the Ganges. // Vi_85.10 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-359597",
    "offset": 554,
    "text": "At Kuśāvarta. // Vi_85.11 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-1cf49d",
    "offset": 584,
    "text": "At Binduka. // Vi_85.12 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-e85f6f",
    "offset": 612,
    "text": "On the Nīla mountain. // Vi_85.13 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-f5af4a",
    "offset": 650,
    "text": "At Kanakhala. // Vi_85.14 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-13a49a",
    "offset": 680,
    "text": "At Kubjāmra. // Vi_85.15 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-1ff413",
    "offset": 709,
    "text": "At Bhṛgutuṅga. // Vi_85.16 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-4f2604",
    "offset": 740,
    "text": "At Kedāra. // Vi_85.17 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-bc8643",
    "offset": 767,
    "text": "At Mahālaya. // Vi_85.18 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-0b4fc7",
    "offset": 796,
    "text": "At Naḍantikā. // Vi_85.19 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-e3ec3a",
    "offset": 826,
    "text": "At Sugandhā. // Vi_85.20 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-f432d3",
    "offset": 855,
    "text": "At Śākambharī. // Vi_85.21 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-ef51c9",
    "offset": 886,
    "text": "At the Phalgutīrtha. // Vi_85.22 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-7889c9",
    "offset": 923,
    "text": "At the Mahāgaṅgā. // Vi_85.23 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-b06c81",
    "offset": 957,
    "text": "In the village of Trihalikā. // Vi_85.24 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-00dbf2",
    "offset": 1002,
    "text": "At Kumāradhārā. // Vi_85.25 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-37988b",
    "offset": 1034,
    "text": "At Prabhāsa. // Vi_85.26 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-bb9f92",
    "offset": 1063,
    "text": "Anywhere on the Sarasvatī, especially. // Vi_85.27 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-51556b",
    "offset": 1118,
    "text": "At Gaṅgādvāra. // Vi_85.28 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-7624ff",
    "offset": 1149,
    "text": "And at Prayāga. // Vi_85.29 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-d931db",
    "offset": 1181,
    "text": "At the confluence of the Ganges and the ocean. // Vi_85.30 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-603468",
    "offset": 1244,
    "text": "Constantly in the Naimiṣa forest. // Vi_85.31 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-c69cde",
    "offset": 1294,
    "text": "And especially in Vārāṇasī. // Vi_85.32 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-32083f",
    "offset": 1338,
    "text": "In the hermitage of Agastya. // Vi_85.33 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-c31107",
    "offset": 1383,
    "text": "In the hermitage of Kaṇva. // Vi_85.34 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-cfd271",
    "offset": 1426,
    "text": "On the Kauśikī. // Vi_85.35 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-72bd3a",
    "offset": 1458,
    "text": "On the bank of the Sarayū. // Vi_85.36 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-18c8df",
    "offset": 1501,
    "text": "At the confluence of the Śoṇa and the Jyotiṣā. // Vi_85.37 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-965109",
    "offset": 1564,
    "text": "On the Śrīparvata mountain. // Vi_85.38 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-628ce3",
    "offset": 1608,
    "text": "At Kālodaka. // Vi_85.39 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-f35751",
    "offset": 1637,
    "text": "At Uttaramānasa. // Vi_85.40 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-44e137",
    "offset": 1670,
    "text": "At Baḍabā. // Vi_85.41 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-d28426",
    "offset": 1697,
    "text": "At Mataṅgavāpī. // Vi_85.42 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-cf7896",
    "offset": 1729,
    "text": "At Saptārṣa. // Vi_85.43 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-43f6b6",
    "offset": 1758,
    "text": "At Viṣṇupada. // Vi_85.44 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-74c8cb",
    "offset": 1788,
    "text": "At Svargamārgapada. // Vi_85.45 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-c59b07",
    "offset": 1824,
    "text": "On the Godāvarī. // Vi_85.46 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-2f4eed",
    "offset": 1857,
    "text": "On the Gomatī. // Vi_85.47 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-e3bb50",
    "offset": 1888,
    "text": "On the Vetravatī. // Vi_85.48 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-b6ff3e",
    "offset": 1922,
    "text": "On the Vipāśā. // Vi_85.49 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-f04ba9",
    "offset": 1953,
    "text": "On the Vitastā. // Vi_85.50 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-97aaf8",
    "offset": 1985,
    "text": "On the bank of the Śatadrū. // Vi_85.51 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-a1cbae",
    "offset": 2029,
    "text": "On the Candrabhāgā. // Vi_85.52 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-ad99c2",
    "offset": 2065,
    "text": "On the Irāvatī. // Vi_85.53 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-546ebd",
    "offset": 2097,
    "text": "On the bank of the Sindhu. // Vi_85.54 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-20e8b8",
    "offset": 2140,
    "text": "In the southern Pañcanada. // Vi_85.55 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-6d3075",
    "offset": 2183,
    "text": "At Ausaja. // Vi_85.56 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-b943c6",
    "offset": 2210,
    "text": "And in these and other sacred bathing places. // Vi_85.57 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-410e5c",
    "offset": 2272,
    "text": "In the best of rivers. // Vi_85.58 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-b99dc9",
    "offset": 2311,
    "text": "In all natural places. // Vi_85.59 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-bf81af",
    "offset": 2350,
    "text": "On riverbanks. // Vi_85.60 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-01bd1f",
    "offset": 2381,
    "text": "At springs. // Vi_85.61 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-9a4526",
    "offset": 2409,
    "text": "On mountains. // Vi_85.62 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-7b6c50",
    "offset": 2439,
    "text": "In groves. // Vi_85.63 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-b64a17",
    "offset": 2466,
    "text": "In forests. // Vi_85.64 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-53f0fc",
    "offset": 2494,
    "text": "In gardens. // Vi_85.65 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-fd2466",
    "offset": 2522,
    "text": "In houses smeared with cow-dung. // Vi_85.66 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-f4909a",
    "offset": 2571,
    "text": "In pleasant places. // Vi_85.67 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-ce8ba6",
    "offset": 2607,
    "text": "And on this subject, there are verses sung by the ancestors (*pitṛgītā gāthā* (पितृगीता गाथा)). // Vi_85.68 //"
  },
  {
    "id": "p-8b6d6c",
    "offset": 2719,
    "text": "> May that being be in our family who will give us handfuls of water, /\n> In rivers with abundant water, especially in cool ones. || Vi_85.69 ||\n>\n> May some excellent man be born in our family, /\n> Who would perform a *śrāddha* (श्राद्ध) for us with a concentrated mind at the Vaṭa tree in Gayāśīrṣa. || Vi_85.70 ||\n>\n> Many sons are to be desired, so that at least one may go to Gayā, /\n> Or perform a horse-sacrifice, or set free a dark-blue bull. || Vi_85.71 ||"
  }
]